-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors line-clamp-1\">鲁皮特（悬崖上的火山岩小镇）</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1 line-clamp-1\">Rupit</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>",
